Package de.fraunhofer.iais.eis

Interface DigitalContent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Described, ModelClass
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AppResource, AudioResource, DataResource, ImageResource, Resource, SoftwareResource, TextResource, VideoResource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AppResourceImpl, AudioResourceImpl, DataResourceImpl, ImageResourceImpl, ResourceImpl, SoftwareResourceImpl, TextResourceImpl, VideoResourceImpl
    public interface DigitalContent
extends Described
    Digital content of a particular type providing hints on its usage, e.g., listening to an Audio, navigating a Structure or accessing a List by an index.
